---
---
<section class="page-container section-spacer">
  <div class="section-rule"></div>
  <p class="eyebrow fade-in">paths</p>
  <h2 class="fade-in-up delay-1" style="max-width: 500px; margin-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);">Same core. Different friction.</h2>
  <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);">
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-2">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">patreon</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; color: var(--color-accent); font-family: var(--font-serif);">$5-15/mo</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Polished installers, auto-updates, priority support. Best for most people.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">One-click Docker installer</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Pre-built PWA</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Auto-update notifications</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Priority support</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Early beta access</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://patreon.com/kxnotes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Get elly</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-3">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">self-host</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-serif);">Free</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Same core, you build the PWA. For tinkerers and privacy maxis.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">docker compose up</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Full source access</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Modify freely</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Runs on Raspberry Pi</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">No account needed</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">View on GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="fade-in-up delay-4">
      <div style="background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;">
        <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">contribute</p>
        <p style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; font-family: var(--font-serif);">Open source</p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Local dev with hot reload. Pull requests welcome.</p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">TypeScript + Python</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">128 tests passing</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">MCP server included</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Design principles in AGENTS.md</li>
          <li style="padding: 0.375rem 0; font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-ink-secondary); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);">Code of Conduct enforced</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/Kxetch/kx-notes/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Read CONTRIBUTING.md</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
